view.name: Seattle Communities Online Inventory
view.attribution: Community Technology, Department of Information Technology, City of Seattle
view.description: This dataset provides a list of websites, blogs, wikis, Twitter feeds, and Facebook pages associated with neighborhood-specific groups and organizations. To add a new site visit http://www.seattle.gov/communitiesonline/addform.htm/jmzd-2qjz

columns.name: Name
columns.description: Name of neighborhood/community group or organization or, if site not associated with a specific group, title of website

columns.name: url
columns.description: web address for the neighborhood/community group or organization, or web address for blog

columns.name: Neighborhood
columns.description: Name of neighborhood within the City of Seattle

columns.name: district
columns.description: district of the City as defined by the Department of Neighborhoods (http://seattle.gov/neighborhoods/nsc/)

columns.name: category
columns.description: short description of the neighborhood/community group or organization, or description of website

columns.description: area of the City as defined by “Neighborhoods on the Net” (http://www.seattle.gov/neighborhoods/net/
